一席霸氣發言也獲粉絲按讚支持，稱這些酸民就是自卑感作祟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-12-23/450/20171223003231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-12-23%2F450%2F20171223003231.jpg&h=8b859629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-12-23/656/20171223003232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-12-23%2F656%2F20171223003232.jpg&h=78a6c5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-12-23/656/20171223003230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-12-23%2F656%2F20171223003230.jpg&h=3a83c290&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>1.台灣男生自己這麼迷日本AV就可以？<br />\n你班台妹係咪拍av先？ 拍既話大把台仔迷<br />\n<br />\n2.一堆娶外籍新娘的就可以？嫖妓嫖越南或韓國妹就可以？啊台灣女生都不能跟外國人在一起只能跟台灣男生在一起？真的是瘋了」<br />\n<br />\n無條件先要娶外國女人， 要俾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多"},{"pid":"a4a3f5c286d3e35a24a6730b2643dbe8690b7893","tid":509864,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"艾莉絲以前好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f31383b99ba76e77fe732747fa4164487cc918d","tid":509864,"uid":97362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"乃哥城城應該日日屌"},{"pid":"70c3352389d1126173d34636f64d8030283fec5f","tid":509864,"uid":52513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"艾莉絲真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061baa61b9bb067fabd76a51cc4b7d1b533c03f8","tid":509864,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT